00274                                           !BCC_ASM
00275                                           MACRO SET_INT_VECTOR
00276                                             push ds
00277                                             xor ax, ax
00278                                             mov ds, ax
00279                                             mov ax, ?3
00280                                             mov ?1*4, ax
00281                                             mov ax, ?2
00282                                             mov ?1*4+2, ax
00283                                             pop ds
00284                                           MEND
00285

00355                       00000106            vgabios_init_func:
00356                                           
00357                                           ;; init vga card
00358 0106           E8         306F              call _init_vga_card
00359                                           
00360                                           ;; init basic bios vars
00361 0109           E8         308C              call _init_bios_area
00362                                           
00363                                           
00364 010C           E8         643B              call _vbe_has_vbe_display
00365 010F           3C                     00    cmp al, #0x00
00366 0111           74           03              je init_no_vbe_display
00367                                           
00368                                           ;; init vbe functions
00369 0113           E8         6452              call _vbe_init
00370                                           
00371                       00000116            init_no_vbe_display:
00372                                           
00373                                           
00374                                           ;; set int10 vect
00375                                             SET_INT_VECTOR(0x10, #0xC000, #vgabios_int10_handler)
 +a   0116           1E                           push ds
 +a   0117           31C0                         xor ax, ax
 +a   0119           8ED8                         mov ds, ax
 +a   011B           B8                   0145    mov ax,  #vgabios_int10_handler
 +a   011E           A3         0040              mov 0x10*4, ax
 +a   0121           B8                   C000    mov ax,  #0xC000
 +a   0124           A3         0042              mov 0x10*4+2, ax
 +a   0127           1F                           pop ds
00376                                           
00377                                           ;; display splash screen
00378 0128           E8         30E4              call _display_splash_screen
00379                                           
00380                                           ;; init video mode and clear the screen
00381 012B           B8                   0003    mov ax,#0x0003
00382 012E           CD                     10    int #0x10
00383                                           
00384                                           ;; copy and activate 8x16 font
00385 0130           B8                   1104    mov ax, #0x1104
00386 0133           B3                     00    mov bl, #0x00
00387 0135           CD                     10    int #0x10
00388 0137           B8                   1103    mov ax, #0x1103
00389 013A           B3                     00    mov bl, #0x00
00390 013C           CD                     10    int #0x10
00391                                           
00392                                           ;; show info
00393 013E           E8         30CF              call _display_info
00394                                           
00395                                           
00396                                           ;; show vbe info
00397 0141           E8         646C              call _vbe_display_info
00398                                           
00399                                           
00400                                           
00401 0144           CB                           retf
00402                                           !BCC_ENDASM
00403                                           ! 275 
00404                                           ! 276 
00405                                           ! 277 
00406                                           ! 278 
00407                                           ! 279 #asm
00408                                           !BCC_ASM
00409                       00000145            vgabios_int10_handler:
00410 0145           9C                           pushf
00411 0146           06                           push es
00412 0147           1E                           push ds
00413 0148           60                           pusha
00414                                           
00415                                           ;; We have to set ds to access the right data segment
00416 0149           BB                   C000    mov bx, #0xc000
00417 014C           8EDB                         mov ds, bx
00418 014E           E8         3104              call _int10_func
00419                                           
00420 0151           61                           popa
00421 0152           1F                           pop ds
00422 0153           07                           pop es
00423 0154           9D                           popf
00424 0155           CF                           iret
00425                                           !BCC_ENDASM

13530                                           ;; switch to color mode and enable CPU access 480 lines
13531 3178           BA                   03C2    mov dx, #0x3C2
13532 317B           B0                     C3    mov al, #0xC3
13533 317D           EE                           outb dx,al
13534                                           
13535                                           ;; more than 64k 3C4/04
13536 317E           BA                   03C4    mov dx, #0x3C4
13537 3181           B0                     04    mov al, #0x04
13538 3183           EE                           outb dx,al
13539

13543 3189           EE                           outb dx,al
13544

13562                                           ! 331 static void init_bios_area()
13563                                           ! 332 {
13564                       00003198            _init_bios_area:
13565                                           ! 333 
13566                                           ! 334   write_word(0x40,0x10,read_word(0x40,0x10)&0xFFCF);
13567 3198           55                         push	bp
13568 3199           89E5                       mov	bp,sp
13569 319B           B8                   0010  mov	ax,*$10
13570 319E           50                         push	ax
13571 319F           B8                   0040  mov	ax,*$40
13572 31A2           50                         push	ax
13573 31A3           E8         2C75            call	_read_word
13574 31A6           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
13575 31A8           24                     CF  and	al,#$CF
13576 31AA           50                         push	ax
13577 31AB           B8                   0010  mov	ax,*$10
13578 31AE           50                         push	ax
13579 31AF           B8                   0040  mov	ax,*$40
13580 31B2           50                         push	ax
13581 31B3           E8         2C90            call	_write_word
13582 31B6           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
13583                                           ! 335 
13584                                           ! 336 
13585                                           ! 337 
13586                                           ! 338

13589 31BB           50                         push	ax
13590 31BC           B8                   0085  mov	ax,#$85
13591 31BF           50                         push	ax
13592 31C0           B8                   0040  mov	ax,*$40
13593 31C3           50                         push	ax

13595 31C7           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
13596                                           ! 340 
13597                                           ! 341 
13598                                           ! 342   write_byte(0x40,0x87,0x60);
13599 31C9           B8                   0060  mov	ax,*$60
13600 31CC           50                         push	ax
13601 31CD           B8                   0087  mov	ax,#$87

20724                                           ! 2077 # 2085 "vgabios.c"
20725                                           ! 2085 static Bit8u find_vga_entry(mode)
20726                                           ! 2086 Bit8u mode;
20727                       00005D1C            _find_vga_entry:
20728                                           ! 2087 {
20729                                           ! 2088  Bit8u i,line=0xFF;
20730 5D1C           55                         push	bp
20731 5D1D           89E5                       mov	bp,sp
20732 5D1F           4C                         dec	sp
20733 5D20           4C                         dec	sp
20734 5D21           B0                     FF  mov	al,#$FF
20735 5D23           8846         FE            mov	-2[bp],al
20736                                           ! 2089  for(i=0;i<=0x13;i++)
20737 5D26           30C0                       xor	al,al
20738 5D28           8846         FF            mov	-1[bp],al
20739                                           ! 2090   if(vga_modes[i].svgamode==mode)
20740 5D2B           EB           23            jmp .1A6
20741                       00005D2D            .1A7:
20742 5D2D           8A46         FF            mov	al,-1[bp]
20743 5D30           30E4                       xor	ah,ah
20744 5D32           B1                     05  mov	cl,*5
20745 5D34           D3E0                       shl	ax,cl
20746 5D36           89C3                       mov	bx,ax
20747 5D38           8A87       0156            mov	al,_vga_modes[bx]
20748 5D3C           3A46         04            cmp	al,4[bp]
20749 5D3F           75           08            jne 	.1A8
20750                       00005D41            .1A9:
20751                                           ! 2091    {line=i;
20752 5D41           8A46         FF            mov	al,-1[bp]
20753 5D44           8846         FE            mov	-2[bp],al
20754                                           ! 2092     break;
20755 5D47           EB           0E            jmp .1A4
20756                                           ! 2093    }
20757                                           ! 2094  return line;
20758                       00005D49            .1A8:
20759                       00005D49            .1A5:
20760 5D49           8A46         FF            mov	al,-1[bp]
20761 5D4C           40                         inc	ax
20762 5D4D           8846         FF            mov	-1[bp],al
20763                       00005D50            .1A6:
20764 5D50           8A46         FF            mov	al,-1[bp]
20765 5D53           3C                     13  cmp	al,*$13
20766 5D55           76           D6            jbe	.1A7
20767                       00005D57            .1AA:
20768                       00005D57            .1A4:
20769 5D57           8A46         FE            mov	al,-2[bp]
20770 5D5A           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
20771 5D5C           5D                         pop	bp
20772 5D5D           C3                         ret
20773                                           ! 2095 }

22592                                           ! 131 
22593                                           ! 132 
22594                                           ! 133 
22595                                           ! 134 
22596                                           ! 135 #asm
22597                                           !BCC_ASM
22598                                           MACRO HALT
22599                                             ;; the HALT macro is called with the line number of the HALT call.
22600                                             ;; The line number is then sent to the 0x501, causing Bochs to
22601                                             ;; print a BX_PANIC message. This will normally halt the simulation
22602                                             ;; with a message such as "BIOS panic at rombios.c, line 4091".
22603                                             ;; However, users can choose to make panics non-fatal and continue.
22604                                             mov dx,#0x501
22605                                             mov ax,#?1
22606                                             out dx,ax
22607                                           MEND
22608                                           !BCC_ENDASM

22612                                           ! 150 static Bit16u dispi_get_id()
22613                                           ! 151 {
22614                                           
22615                       0000637F            _dispi_get_id:
22616                                           ! 152   outw(0xFF80,0x0);
22617 637F           55                         push	bp
22618 6380           89E5                       mov	bp,sp
22619 6382           31C0                       xor	ax,ax
22620 6384           50                         push	ax
22621 6385           B8                   FF80  mov	ax,#$FF80
22622 6388           50                         push	ax
22623 6389           E8         FAF8            call	_outw
22624 638C           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
22625                                           ! 153   return inw(0xFF81);
22626 638E           B8                   FF81  mov	ax,#$FF81
22627 6391           50                         push	ax
22628 6392           E8         FAD4            call	_inw
22629 6395           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
22630 6397           5D                         pop	bp
22631 6398           C3                         ret
22632                                           ! 154 }

22927                                           ! 251 
22928                                           ! 252 static ModeInfoListItem* mode_info_find_mode(mode)
22929                                           ! 253   Bit16u mode;
22930                       00006512            _mode_info_find_mode:
22931                                           ! 254 {
22932                                           ! 255   ModeInfoListItem *cur_info=&mode_info_list;
22933 6512           55                         push	bp
22934 6513           89E5                       mov	bp,sp
22935 6515           4C                         dec	sp
22936 6516           4C                         dec	sp
22937 6517           BB                   5FD4  mov	bx,#_mode_info_list
22938 651A           895E         FE            mov	-2[bp],bx
22939                                           ! 256 
22940                                           ! 257   while (cur_info->mode != 0xFFFF)
22941                                           ! 258   {
22942 651D           EB           1A            jmp .1C6
22943                       0000651F            .1C7:
22944                                           ! 259     if (cur_info->mode == mode)
22945 651F           8B5E         FE            mov	bx,-2[bp]
22946 6522           8B1F                       mov	bx,[bx]
22947 6524           3B5E         04            cmp	bx,4[bp]
22948 6527           75           07            jne 	.1C8
22949                       00006529            .1C9:
22950                                           ! 260     {
22951                                           ! 261       return cur_info;
22952 6529           8B46         FE            mov	ax,-2[bp]
22953 652C           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
22954 652E           5D                         pop	bp
22955 652F           C3                         ret
22956                                           ! 262     }
22957                                           ! 263 
22958                                           ! 264     cur_info++;
22959                       00006530            .1C8:
22960 6530           8B5E         FE            mov	bx,-2[bp]
22961 6533           83C3                   44  add	bx,*$44
22962 6536           895E         FE            mov	-2[bp],bx
22963                                           ! 265   }
22964                                           ! 266 
22965                                           ! 267   return 0;
22966                       00006539            .1C6:
22967 6539           8B5E         FE            mov	bx,-2[bp]
22968 653C           8B1F                       mov	bx,[bx]
22969 653E           81FB                 FFFF  cmp	bx,#$FFFF
22970 6542           75           DB            jne	.1C7
22971                       00006544            .1CA:
22972                       00006544            .1C5:
22973 6544           31C0                       xor	ax,ax
22974 6546           89EC                       mov	sp,bp
22975 6548           5D                         pop	bp
